title: Hawkwind 1970-05 Port Talbot -FLAC (POOR QUALITY)
description:
This is the earliest Hawkwind audience recording currently known to exist.

QUALITY: dire! Rated 4/10.

This is probably for die-hard Hawkwind fans only, who want to hear how an early set was put together. Everyone else should avoid it. You have been warned!!

Run-time 30 mins.
